  "text": "More complex production function approaches incorporating the role of resilience measures have been implemented by Rose, Oladosu, and Shu-Yi [CITATION_1] . Other studies have also developed mixed approaches combining macroeconomic data with consumer surveys (Reichel, Schmidthaler, and Schneider [CITATION_2] ).",
